<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 54–55" captionStartId="F17" captionText="Figures 54 - 55. 54 Semiardistomis propinquus (Putzeys) 55 Semiardistomis viridis (Say). Dorsal aspect. Scale bar 1 mm." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/19675" pageId="31" pageNumber="50">Fig. 55</figureCitation>
