<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="50" type="habitat and activity">
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="50">Habitat and activity.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="50">
I collected this species in the &quot;Eagle trail&quot; at the Grassy Waters Preserve in West Palm Beach on April 2, 2011. Adults were active during the day on sandy margins of a fresh water pond (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 56" captionStartId="F18" captionText="Figure 56. Habitat of Semiardistomis viridis (Say) at Grassy Waters Preserve, West Palm Beach, Florida, USA" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/19676" pageId="31" pageNumber="50">Fig. 56</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
